data.title: Moe should be on Newbury Street. Awesome food!
data.text: This is a hidden gem in Malden. Moe has the best panini and subs in the greater Boston area. Even the plain grilled cheese is to die for.  My favorite is the pesto mayo chicken. Moe and his crew are friendly and pleasant. The prices are more than reasonable. It would be hard to be disappointed.
